
Hero Section – Catchy headline, brief description, and a call-to-action button.
Services Section – List of cleaning services with icons.
Why Choose Us – Highlight key benefits (e.g., eco-friendly, reliable staff).
Testimonials – Customer reviews for social proof.
Contact Form – Easy way for clients to request a quote.
Footer – Social media links and contact details.


